{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "b7e2f1a0-c3d4-4e56-89ab-cd12ef345678",
        "name": "Tirumala AI — SrivariAI Chat",
        "description": "Tests for the Gemini-powered SrivariAI assistant.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/ai/chat`\n\nAll requests are **public** — no auth token needed.\n\n## Request shape\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"<user question>\",\n  \"history\": []   // optional — prior turns for multi-turn chat\n}\n```\n\n## Response shape\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"reply\": \"<AI answer>\",\n  \"isOffTopic\": false\n}\n```\n`isOffTopic: true` means the question was outside the Tirumala scope and the AI politely declined.\n\n## History turn shape\nEach item in `history` must be:\n```json\n{ \"role\": \"user\" | \"model\", \"content\": \"<string>\" }\n```\n\nSet the `baseUrl` collection variable to your running server (default: `http://localhost:3000`).",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://localhost:3000",
            "type": "string"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "On-Topic Questions",
            "description": "Questions that are within the Tirumala / TTD scope. `isOffTopic` should always be `false` in these responses.",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Darshan — How to book SED ticket",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"message\": \"How do I book a Special Entry Darshan (SED) ticket online? What is the cost?\",\n    \"history\": []\n}",
                            "options": {
                                "raw": {
                                    "language": "json"
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat",
                            "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                            "path": ["api", "ai", "chat"]
                        },
                        "description": "Ask SrivariAI about SED (Special Entry Darshan) ticket booking process and cost."
                    }
                },
